<template>
  <Header />
  <router-view />
</template>

<script>
import Header from './components/Header.vue';

export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    Header,
  },
  async beforeMount() {
    let accessToken = this.$store.getters.getAccessToken;
    if(accessToken != null)
    {
    const response = await axios.get('http://localhost:8080/api/auth//userByRefreshToken/', {
            token: accessToken,
        });
      }
  },
}
</script>

<style>
#app {
  font-family: Avenir, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-align: center;
  color: #273043;
}
a
{
  text-decoration: none;
  color: inherit;
}
</style>
